wikipedia_page.main: Ryan Donnelly (born 23 October 1991) is a Scottish footballer, who plays for Gartcairn Juniors in the Scottish Junior Football Association, West Region. He first played for Airdrie United and has also played for Brechin City, Albion Rovers and Ayr United.
